EIP_712-and ECDSA with Frontend

First deploy erc20 Mytoken with permit function
and Deploy permit.js it will log all the required details which can be used in permit function in smart contract
Can use frontend to do the whole process in one place 

ECDSA
Deploy Erc20ForEcdsa.sol
Then deployEcdsa.js which will send deploy Erc20 Ecdsa tokens and hold some tokens
provide reciever and amount to deployEcdsa.js and it will return a signature 
The reciever can use the signature to claim the tokens from Erc20 ECDSA contract by triggering claim token

